
<<TableOfContents()>>



= P-Close - Problems Close to P =

----
CategoryClassical 

== Description ==

{{{#!description

The class of decision problems solvable by a polynomial-time algorithm that outputs the wrong answer on only a sparse (that is, polynomially-bounded) set of instances.}}}

